quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,"Mi ahodaano e mon, onon …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama, wonnde wata on rewu seytaane? Tawde pellet, ko o ga√±o mon …ìanngu…óo"
  36,61,"[Mi yamiri on] kadi rewugol Lam. Ko ngol woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  36,62,Gom…óii o majjinii tagu …óuu…óungu e mon. E on wonaano haqqiloo…ìe
  36,63,"Ko ngee woni Jahannama, nge wonano…óon fodaneede ngen"
  36,64,"Naatiree nge hannde, sabu kon ko yeddirayno…óon"
  36,65,"Hannde, Men notay e kunndule ma…ì…ìe …óen, juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yewta Men, koy…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen kadi seeditoo e kon ko …ìe wonunoo e faggitagol"
  36,66,"Si Men yi…óuno, Men mehayno gite ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe adondira e laawol ngol. Kono ko honno …ìe yiirata"
  36,67,"Si Men yi…óuno kadi, Men montayno …ìe e nokku ma…ì…ìe on; hara …ìe hattantaa fe∆¥∆¥ugol …ìe yiltotaako"
  36,68,"Kala mo Men juutni nguurndam mun, Men yiltitay mo e tagu ngun. E …ìee haqqiltaa"
  36,69,"Men anndinaali mo (kanko Muhammadu) gim…ói; …óum haananaa mo. [Deftere] nden wonaali, si wanaa jantoore e janngeteende …ìanngunde"
  36,70,"fii yo o jertin nde, on won…óo wuur…óo (…ìernde), Konngol lepte ngol jojja e heefer…ìe …ìen"
  36,71,"E …ìe yi'aali, wonnde Men tagiranii …ìe neemoraa…ói, e ko juu…óe Amen golli, hara hi…ìe jeyinoo…ói"
  36,72,"Men eltani …ìe …ói: no e majji …ói …ìe wa…ó…óotoo, no e majji …ói …ìe √±aamata"
  36,73,"hino woodani …ìe ton, nafooje e njaram. E …ìee kan yettataa (Mo)"
  36,74,"∆Åe jogitorii gaanin Alla rewetee…ói, jortagol …ìe faabeedee"
  36,75,∆äi hattanaa faabagol …ìe; ko …ìe konu tawneteengu e majji
  36,76,"Wata konngol ma…ì…ìe sunine. Pellet, Me…óen anndi ko …ìe suu…óata e ko …ìe fe√±√±inta"
  36,77,"E ne…ó…óanke on yi'aali, wonnde Men tagirii mo e to…ì…ìere maniiyu? Kono tawaa mo ko o wennjoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  36,78,"O fiyani Men misal, kono o yejjiti tageede makko; o wi'i: \"Ko hommbo wuurnitata ∆¥i'e …óen, si …óe rappii"
  36,79,"Maaku: \"Ko wuurnitoowo …óe, ko tagu…óo …óe On ka laawol aranol. Ko Kanko woni anndu…óo fii kala tagu"
  36,80,"On wa…óan…óo on yiite, iwde e le…ó…óe kecce, tawa ko e majje hu…ì…ìirton nge"
  36,81,"Kere tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin wonaali ha…ótan…óo tagugol yeru ma…ì…ìe? ∆äum ko pellet! Ko Kanko woni ∆äuu…óu…óo tageefo, Anndu…óo"
  36,82,"Anndon fiyaaku Makko On, si O faandanike huunde, ko O wi'anay nde tun: \"Laato\", nde laatoo"
  36,83,Senayee woodanii On Mo laamateeri kala huunde woni e juu…óe Mun! Ko ka Makko ruttete…óon
  37,1,Mi woondirii saffiniraa…ói …óin saffaaji
  37,2,Mi woondirii soggiray…ói (duule) …óin soggugol
  37,3,"Mi woondirii janngiray…ói …óin, anndintinorgol"
  37,4,"Pellet, rewetee…óo mon On, ko bajjo"
  37,5,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, Jey…óo kadi fu…óir…óe …óen"
  37,6,"Men cu…óirii kammu (hikkii ngu) aduna ngun: cu…óaari koode …óen"
  37,7,e reenirgol (ngu) kala seytaane ra…óaandu
  37,8,"∆äi ha…ótanaaka he…óitagol mbatu [Malaa'ika'en] toowu ngu ngun; tawde hi…ói feroree e kala ba≈ã≈ãe"
  37,9,"ka ra…óagol (…ói). Hino woodani …ói kadi, lepte duumii…óe"
  37,10,"Si wanaa ndun bifti ndu e majji, jilannde [haala], ndu rewniree hoodere tufaynde"
  37,11,"Lamndo …ìe: si ko kam…ìe …ìuri sa…ótude tagude kaa ko …ìen …ìe Men tagi? Men tagirii …ìe kam…ìe, loopal narnungal"
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, hi…ìe jalnora"
  37,13,"Si …ìe waajaama, …ìe waajitortaa"
  37,14,"si …ìe yi'ii maande, …ìe jalkita"
  37,15,"…ìe wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  37,16,"Eyoo si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, haray ko men immintinoytee…ìe"
  37,17,Baabiraa…ìe amen adinoo…ìe …ìen kadi e minen
  37,18,"Maaku: \"Pellet! Hara le ko on hoynaa…ìe"
  37,19,"Anndon …óum, ko wuttaandu wooturu pet, tawee jaka yoo, hi…ìe ndaara"
  37,20,"∆Åe wi'a: Ee bone amen ! Ko ndee woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe"
  37,21,"Ko ndee woni √ëalaande √±aawoore, ko fennayno…óon fii mun"